### Feature: Dynamic Squad Task Combinations

**Implementation Details:**
- Reworked [SquadsView](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#2004-2597) in [DailyMeetingView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx) to identify the exact subset of squad members assigned to each task.
- Tasks are now grouped by these assigned subsets (e.g., A & B & C, or A & B, or B & C).
- Groups are sorted descending by size (tasks shared by all 3 people appear at the top, followed by tasks shared by 2 people, and finally individual tasks).
- The "Shared Tasks" headers are dynamically generated based on the specific combination of people involved (e.g., "Shared: Person A, Person C").

